comments: Murray (DEN) and Hart (NOP) engage and disengage with one another off-ball.
Adams (NOP) contests Murray's (DEN) driving shot attempt and marginal arm contact occurs after the release.
Jokic (DEN) places his arm against Hart (NOP) and marginal contact occurs during the rebound.  Jokic does not dislodge Hart from his position.
Adams (NOP) has a grasp of Jokic's (DEN) jersey as they engage with one another during rebounding and marginal contact occurs as Adams back-taps the ball.
Porter Jr. (DEN) extends his hand forward and marginal contact occurs with Ingram's (NOP) front during his drive toward the lane.
Jokic (DEN) jumps vertically and is turned by the contact with Ingram (NOP), which Jokic absorbs during the driving shot attempt.
Millsap (DEN) maintains his left foot as his pivot after picking up his dribble.
Adams (NOP) and Jokic (DEN) engage and disengage with one another off ball.
Ingram (NOP) and Millsap (DEN) engage and disengage with one another off ball.
Jokic (DEN) brings his off-arm toward Adams' (NOP) side and marginal contact occurs as Jokic starts his drive.

Adams (NOP) establishes himself in a screening position in Porter Jr.'s (DEN) path and after absorbing the initial contact, re-establishes himself in position by moving in the same direction as Porter Jr.
Williamson (NOP) moves toward Millsap (DEN) and marginal contact occurs with Millsap's back as he secures the rebound.
Adams (NOP) firms up in his defensive position and absorbs the body contact made with Jokic (DEN) during his drive toward the lane.
Adams (NOP) initiates contact with Jokic's (DEN) right arm during his upward shooting motion and affects his jump shot attempt.
Porter Jr. (DEN) moves forward and marginal contact occurs with Ingram's (NOP) front during the drive.
Jokic (DEN) maintains a legal guarding position as incidental foot-to-foot contact occurs with Ingram (NOP) at the end of the drive.
Alexander-Walker (NOP) extends his right leg unnaturally into Barton (DEN) on the jump shot attempt.
Barton (DEN) cleanly blocks Alexander-Walker's (NOP) jump shot attempt.
Murray (DEN) and Alexander-Walker (NOP) engage and disengage with one another during the inbound.
Adams (NOP) establishes himself in a screening position in Porter Jr.'s (DEN) path and absorbs the contact.
Porter Jr. (DEN) and Ingram (NOP) engage with one another during the inbound and disengage as they move over the screen.
Alexander-Walker (NOP) and Murray (DEN) come together at the same spot and marginal contact occurs with Murray's front as Alexander-Walker naturally releases away.
Murray (DEN) is turning slightly toward Ingram (NOP) and marginal contact occurs as Ingram is passing the ball.
Correctly called 24 second violation on NOP.
Williamson (NOP) commits a take foul on Barton (DEN).
Alexander-Walker (NOP) commits a take foul on Barton (DEN).

call_type: Turnover:  Out of Bounds - Bad Pass Turn
comments: Ingram (NOP) touches the ball last before it goes out of bounds.
